Package: tableFilter
Title: A table widget based on Max Guglielmi's "HTML Table Filter Generator" and D3.js
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Siegmund", email = "thomas.siegmund@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: tableFilter provides a powerful and flexible HTML table widget for use with the htmlwidgets R library. It allows R users to create HTML tables with functions for advanced filtering and sorting. It also allows for the colouring of table cells based on their values.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.1)
Imports: htmlwidgets (>= 0.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Enhances: rmarkdown (>= 0.3.3), shiny (>= 0.10.2.1)
